28:48.030 --> 28:49.410
Nezuko!

28:52.580 --> 28:54.670
He hit the wall all of a sudden!

28:55.000 --> 28:57.170
Young Kamado, hang in there!

28:57.170 --> 28:58.460
Is he dead? Is he dead?

28:58.460 --> 28:59.170
Idiot!

29:00.000 --> 29:01.210
Are you all right?

29:01.210 --> 29:02.550
Stay with us!

29:03.800 --> 29:05.680
Thank goodness...

29:06.930 --> 29:08.300
Nezuko...

29:09.890 --> 29:11.520
Thank goodness.

29:32.500 --> 29:34.330
I can't take it any more!

29:37.670 --> 29:39.290
I'm so sorry!

29:39.290 --> 29:41.050
