must've beheaded the main body!

30:20.040 --> 30:21.380
Toshikuni?

30:23.000 --> 30:24.670
I'm coming in, all right?

30:25.920 --> 30:27.130
Oh my...

30:30.510 --> 30:32.600
What's gotten into you, Toshikuni?

30:32.600 --> 30:34.970
Making such a mess...

30:35.270 --> 30:37.520
I see that you've been doing some research.

30:37.890 --> 30:40.270
You can't find the book that you need?

30:40.770 --> 30:43.110
I'll help you find it.

30:43.110 --> 30:45.150
But first, take a break.

30:45.150 --> 30:46.990
Let's have some tea.

30:47.490 --> 30:49.280
At last...

30:49.570 --> 30:51.240
What's that?

30:51.990 --> 30:57.120
At last, someone able
to withstand the sun has appeared!

30:57.120 --> 31:00.120
Good work, Hantengu!

31:00.500 --> 31:02.960
Well, you certainly seem
to be enjoying yourself.

31:02.960 --> 31:05.760
Perhaps it's the stories
you've been readingâ€”

31:06.090 --> 31:06.920
Huh?

31:12.180 --> 31:15.010
Huh? Madam?

31:15.010 --> 31:16.680
What happened...

31:16.680 --> 31:18.520
to your head?

31:18.890 --> 31:20.810
Now...

31:20.810 --> 31:24.570
there's no need to search
for the Blue Spider Lily.

31:24.570 --> 31:25.530
Madam...

31:26.150 --> 31:27.940
That took so long.

31:27.940 --> 31:32.530
But it was for this reason,
for this reason, for one thousand years...

31:32.870 --> 31:37.790
that I've continued
to increase my kind unwillingly!

31:45.750 --> 31:51.430
A rare constitution that never showed up
even among the Twelve Kizuki.

31:51.430 --> 31:53.550
The chosen demon.

31:53.930 --> 31:57.310
If I devour that girl and absorb her...

31:57.310 --> 32:00.940
I, too, will be able to conquer the sun!

32:00.940 --> 32:03.940
You murderer! You murderer!
You monster!

32:03.940 --> 32:06.400
Master! Master!

32:06.400 --> 32:07.230
Maâ€”

32:21.540 --> 32:24.040
<i>Now that I think of it, it was on that day.</i>

32:26.000 --> 32:29.050
<i>It all started one thousand years ago.</i>

32:29.550 --> 32:33.550
<i>The era was still called Heian back then.</i>

32:34.640 --> 32:36.550
If I may, sir...

32:36.930 --> 32:41.060
Your medicine is ready for you now.

32:41.810 --> 32:43.810
You inept doctor...

32:44.980 --> 32:50.150
That said, this inept doctor
is the only one I have to lean on.

32:51.690 --> 32:53.200
What will become of me...

32:53.530 --> 32:55.450
if I don't take this?

32:56.160 --> 32:58.120
As you know...

32:58.120 --> 33:00.370
you will not live...

33:00.370 --> 33:02.830
to see your 20th birthday.

33:03.160 --> 33:05.120
I am doing all I can...

33:05.120 --> 33:07.840
to help you live...

33:07.840 --> 33:10.340
even a little longer.

33:11.300 --> 33:12.470
All right, fine.

33:12.470 --> 33:14.130
That's enough.

33:16.760 --> 33:19.100
<i>It won't work anyway.</i>

33:24.100 --> 33:25.900
<i>Ah...</i>

33:25.900 --> 33:27.610
<i>I want to destroy them!</i>

33:27.610 --> 33:30.280
<i>Every living being!</i>

33:32.320 --> 33:35.320
<i>No matter how many times
he examines me...</i>

33:35.320 --> 33:37.780
<i>or administers that medicine...</i>

33:38.200 --> 33:41.290
<i>nothing can stop
my symptoms from worsening.</i>

33:55.840 --> 33:58.340
Death is all you deserve!

33:58.340 --> 34:00.560
You damn incompetent doctor!

34:01.220 --> 34:06.900
<i>But then I realized that this doctor's
medicine was working...</i>

34:06.900 --> 34:10.440
<i>not longer after I'd killed him.</i>

34:11.480 --> 34:14.570
<i>My body was bursting with energy...</i>

34:14.570 --> 34:18.780
<i>and I thought that I'd gained
a durable physique...</i>

34:18.780 --> 34:21.200
<i>but there was one problem.</i>

34:21.950 --> 34:25.290
<i>I couldn't walk in the sunlight.</i>

34:35.050 --> 34:37.260
<i>I could tell.</i>

34:37.260 --> 34:40.680
<i>That if exposed to sunlight, I would die.</i>

34:50.310 --> 34:53.650
<i>I began to crave human flesh and blood.</i>

34:54.110 --> 34:55.650
<i>To remedy that...</i>

34:55.650 --> 34:57.950
<i>all I had to do was devour humans.</i>

35:00.780 --> 35:05.080
If anyone stands in your way,
just eliminate them.

35:05.540 --> 35:07.870
That's all there is to it.

35:07.870 --> 35:09.290
Come back here!

35:09.290 --> 35:12.130
You cursed demon who disrupts
the peace of the capital!

35:14.920 --> 35:16.420
Are you...

35:17.920 --> 35:20.260
talking about me?

35:34.230 --> 35:36.860
<i>I had gained power.</i>

35:37.190 --> 35:39.610
<i>Eternal power!</i>

35:42.660 --> 35:44.160
<i>But...</i>

35:44.160 --> 35:48.660
<i>having to restrict my movements
during the day was humiliating...</i>

35:48.660 --> 35:51.750
<i>and my anger only grew.</i>

35:52.250 --> 35:57.510
<i>I began to seek a body
that wouldn't perish in the sunlight.</i>

35:58.510 --> 36:01.890
<i>I examined the compounds
for the doctor's elixir,</i>

36:01.890 --> 36:04.470
<i>but perhaps because it was still
in the experimental stages,</i>

36:04.470 --> 36:10.440
<i>I couldn't figure out how to make
the medicine called "Blue Spider Lily."</i>

36:10.850 --> 36:16.610
<i>It did seem to contain actual
blue-colored Spider Lilies...</i>

36:16.610 --> 36:23.620
<i>but as for where this Blue Spider Lily bloomed
or whether or not it could be cultivated...</i>

36:24.160 --> 36:27.160
<i>no one knew but the doctor I'd killed.</i>

36:27.160 --> 36:30.870
<i>I searched all over Japan
but failed to find it.</i>

36:32.000 --> 36:36.170
<i>In order to become truly immortal...</i>

36:36.630 --> 36:39.130
<i>finding the Blue Spider Lily...</i>

36:39.130 --> 36:43.260
<i>and someone who had the ability
to survive the sunlight...</i>

36:43.680 --> 36:47.640
<i>Those two have been my top priorities.</i>

36:50.730 --> 36:52.640
<i>And at last...</i>

36:53.020 --> 36:54.650
<i>I've found her!</i>

36:59.190 --> 37:02.780
<i>Since that girl has conquered the sun...</i>

37:03.110 --> 37:07.030
<i>there's no longer any reason
to increase my kind.</i>

37:07.330 --> 37:09.330
<i>I will absorb her...</i>

37:09.330 --> 37:13.420
<i>and then I will conquer the sunlight.</i>

37:14.000 --> 37:16.380
<i>I will get my hands on Nezuko...</i>

37:16.380 --> 37:20.760
<i>and become a perfect being!</i>

37:24.630 --> 37:27.260
Tanjiro, are you all right?

37:29.930 --> 37:31.100
Hey...

37:31.100 --> 37:33.980
T-Tokito...

37:35.150 --> 37:36.560
Thank goodness...

37:36.560 --> 37:37.940
you're safe!

37:38.360 --> 37:40.940
Thank you for my sword!

37:41.820 --> 37:44.070
I should be thanking you.

37:44.070 --> 37:47.820
Because of you, I recovered
something precious that I'd lost.

37:48.200 --> 37:50.830
Huh? No...

37:50.830 --> 37:52.830
but I didn't do anything.

37:53.750 --> 37:55.120
It's all right.

37:55.120 --> 37:57.460
Thank you from the bottom of my heart!

37:58.420 --> 38:00.710
Tokito...

38:01.300 --> 38:04.800
Anyway, what's going on with Nezuko?

38:05.180 --> 38:07.010
Well, actually...

38:07.010 --> 38:09.100
Why, you...

38:12.180 --> 38:14.350
What did you do with my sword?

38:14.350 --> 38:15.730
Calm down!

38:16.020 --> 38:16.940
Huh?

38:17.650 --> 38:18.860
Mr. Haganezuka?

38:19.190 --> 38:23.490
I asked you what happened
to the sword I was honing!

38:23.490 --> 38:25.700
I used it to fight an Upper Rank!

38:25.700 --> 38:27.780
Yeah, to fight?

38:27.780 --> 38:29.370
To fight, and...

38:29.370 --> 38:30.450
Huh?

38:30.450 --> 38:31.990
What happened then?

38:31.990 --> 38:34.000
I blacked out, and...

38:34.620 --> 38:36.500
Oh, the sword? I've got itâ€”

38:36.500 --> 38:37.620
You broke it, right?

38:38.330 --> 38:39.540
Uh, no.

38:39.540 --> 38:42.300
You broke it, didn't you? Tell me the truth!

38:42.300 --> 38:44.340
Tell! Me! The! Truth!

38:44.340 --> 38:46.300
I didn't... I didn't...

38:46.300 --> 38:47.680
No, it's right here!

38:47.680 --> 38:49.510
I'm going to kill you!

38:49.510 --> 38:51.050
Nezuko, run!

38:51.050 --> 38:52.010
Run!

38:52.010 --> 38:53.220
You're not getting away!

38:53.520 --> 38:55.890
Mr. Haganezuka! Calm down!

38:55.890 --> 38:57.810
The sword is right here!
Come back here!
Come back here!

38:57.810 --> 38:58.350
Like hell, I'll calm down!
The sword is right here!

38:58.350 --> 38:58.940
Like hell, I'll calm down!

38:58.940 --> 38:59.650
- Come on, come on!
- You guys!
Like hell, I'll calm down!

38:59.650 --> 39:01.560
- Come on, come on!
- You guys!

39:02.150 --> 39:04.480
You guys!

39:07.700 --> 39:09.490
Ms. Kanroji!

39:17.710 --> 39:20.540
We won! We won!

39:20.540 --> 39:22.630
We all won together!

39:22.630 --> 39:25.880
So amazing! We're all alive!

39:26.170 --> 39:28.470
Thank goodness!

39:29.050 --> 39:31.260
Yes, thank goodness!

39:35.020 --> 39:35.810
Huh?

39:35.810 --> 39:36.850
Yes...

39:36.850 --> 39:39.020
thank goodness!

39:40.400 --> 39:42.860
Whaaaaat?

39:50.780 --> 39:52.070
Tanjiro!

39:52.570 --> 39:53.580
Yes?

39:56.450 --> 39:59.250
Thank goodness!

40:00.250 --> 40:02.000
She's talking...

40:02.000 --> 40:04.250
but her eyes and fangs are the same...

40:04.630 --> 40:07.380
so I'm not sure what's going on, but I...

40:07.710 --> 40:09.880
I'm so glad that Nezuko's alive!

40:10.260 --> 40:12.470
Thank goodness she's alive!

40:13.930 --> 40:15.600
Yes! Yes!

40:16.010 --> 40:18.140
Thank goodness!

40:18.930 --> 40:21.640
Thank goodness!

40:22.230 --> 40:24.270
Thank goodness!

40:24.810 --> 40:27.030
Thank goodness!

40:29.070 --> 40:31.450
Thank goodness!

40:32.280 --> 40:33.740
<i>Tanjiro...</i>

40:34.410 --> 40:37.910
<i>I thank you for providing me
with the Twelve Kizuki's and Nezuko's blood...</i>

40:37.910 --> 40:41.290
<i>and for helping me with my research.</i>

40:46.090 --> 40:50.050
<i>The man in Asakusa
who was turned into a demon by Muzan...</i>

40:50.050 --> 40:52.510
<i>has regained his sense of self.</i>

40:52.970 --> 40:55.300
<i>It's thanks to Nezuko's blood.</i>

40:56.430 --> 40:58.810
<i>Released from Muzan's control...</i>

40:59.180 --> 41:02.310
<i>he can live on a small amount of blood.</i>

41:02.600 --> 41:06.690
<i>The transformation of Nezuko's blood
surprises me.</i>

41:06.980 --> 41:12.700
<i>In such a short time, the components
of her blood have changed again and again.</i>

41:22.160 --> 41:23.620
<i>All this time...</i>

41:23.620 --> 41:25.500
<i>I have been thinking.</i>

41:26.290 --> 41:29.380
<i>Why it is that Nezuko has yet to regain
her sense of self...</i>

41:29.710 --> 41:33.260
<i>and remains in a child-like state?</i>

41:33.930 --> 41:35.260
<i>I believe that...</i>

41:35.260 --> 41:37.180
<i>in Nezuko's mind...</i>

41:37.180 --> 41:40.020
<i>there's something more important
than regaining her sense of self...</i>

41:40.020 --> 41:43.230
<i>something that she needs to prioritize.</i>

41:45.440 --> 41:46.480
Yushiro?

41:46.770 --> 41:47.650
Yushiro?

41:48.860 --> 41:50.860
Yes, Lady Tamayo?

41:50.860 --> 41:52.280
What can I do for you?

41:52.280 --> 41:54.030
Can you summon Chachamaru for me?

41:58.830 --> 42:02.160
Chachamaru is ready to go now.

42:08.250 --> 42:11.630
Give my regards
to Tanjiro and Nezuko, okay?

42:19.930 --> 42:21.310
<i>Tanjiro...</i>

42:21.640 --> 42:25.520
<i>This is pure speculation on my part.</i>

42:26.730 --> 42:29.190
<i>But I believe that it won't be long...</i>

42:30.230 --> 42:33.360
<i>before Nezuko can conquer the sun.</i>

42:42.910 --> 42:43.870
Right!

42:47.920 --> 42:49.040
Thanks!

42:49.750 --> 42:51.130
Understood!

43:01.430 --> 43:03.770
Lord Tecchin!

43:04.390 --> 43:06.390
Oh! Kotetsu!

43:07.190 --> 43:10.900
Mr. Tanjiro's leaving the village,
so he'd like to say goodbye.

43:14.110 --> 43:15.320
Mr. Tanjiro?

43:19.410 --> 43:22.330
HYOTTOKO

43:22.330 --> 43:24.740
Are you feeling all right?
HYOTTOKO

43:24.740 --> 43:28.120
Yes! Thank you
for all that you did for me.
HYOTTOKO

43:28.120 --> 43:29.290
And thank you.
HYOTTOKO

43:29.290 --> 43:31.500
You even provided me
with this cart.
HYOTTOKO

43:32.000 --> 43:34.960
I'm the one who should be thanking you.

43:34.960 --> 43:37.670
You did a good job protecting this village!

43:37.670 --> 43:39.180
I'm grateful to you!

43:39.510 --> 43:42.600
I wasn't able to do that much on my own.

43:43.050 --> 43:44.810
It was everyone pulling together!

43:45.220 --> 43:46.850
Our combined strength...

43:46.850 --> 43:51.150
and that sword that's been connecting us
to centuries of hopes until today.

43:51.150 --> 43:53.940
That's why we were able to defeat
those Upper Rank demons.

43:54.270 --> 43:55.780
Yes, yes.

43:55.780 --> 43:57.440
You're right.

43:58.240 --> 44:00.110
And where's your sister?

44:00.950 --> 44:02.410
She's asleep.

44:02.410 --> 44:04.580
Since I really exhausted her.

44:12.580 --> 44:13.840
I see!

44:13.840 --> 44:16.420
I'm truly glad that she's all right!

44:17.760 --> 44:19.010
Yes!

44:20.220 --> 44:21.380
Huh?

44:24.550 --> 44:29.230
Hey, Kanamori! Is that Hotaru
lurking around over there?

44:29.230 --> 44:30.480
Yes.

44:30.480 --> 44:32.270
What is he doing?

44:32.270 --> 44:34.980
He seems to think that he's hiding...

44:34.980 --> 44:39.150
but apparently, he can't forgive Tanjiro
for using a sword before it was fully honed.

44:39.150 --> 44:40.650
Huh?

44:40.950 --> 44:43.280
What am I going to do with that guy?

44:43.280 --> 44:44.370
Hotaru!

44:44.370 --> 44:46.120
Come over here a second!

44:48.750 --> 44:51.500
I said, come over here!

44:56.800 --> 44:58.050
Hotaru!

44:58.630 --> 45:00.470
I'm telling you, it's all his fault.

45:01.340 --> 45:02.340
Ouch!

45:02.630 --> 45:04.260
Right? Am I right?

45:04.260 --> 45:04.890
Am I right?

45:04.890 --> 45:05.350
Hey! Come on... Hey!
Am I right?

45:05.350 --> 45:06.300
Sorry!
Hey! Come on... Hey!

45:06.300 --> 45:07.560
Ouch! That hurts!
Hey! Come on... Hey!

45:07.560 --> 45:07.890
Ouch! That hurts!

45:07.890 --> 45:08.720
Hotaru!

45:09.020 --> 45:11.690
But... if Mr. Tanjiro
and the others hadn't come...

45:11.690 --> 45:14.230
I'm sure the village
would've been destroyed!

45:14.560 --> 45:16.440
Ow! Ow!

45:16.440 --> 45:17.400
Hah!

45:19.610 --> 45:20.820
Now, Hotaru...

45:21.190 --> 45:24.610
the real reason you came here
was to speak to Tanjiro...

45:24.610 --> 45:27.160
who came all the way here, right?

45:30.830 --> 45:32.370
Mr. Haganezuka...

45:32.370 --> 45:36.210
Thank you for always
taking care of my sword!

45:36.630 --> 45:38.340
I came to this village...

45:38.340 --> 45:40.590
because I wanted to thank you for that.

45:42.550 --> 45:48.050
I-I'll reforge your sword for you,
so wait for it at the Butterfly Mansion.

45:48.560 --> 45:50.560
You're going to repair it for me?

45:50.560 --> 45:53.060
Don't you want me to fix it?

45:53.060 --> 45:54.600
Thank you very much!

45:54.940 --> 45:57.060
S-S-Sure.

45:57.770 --> 45:58.980
Mr. Haganezuka...

45:58.980 --> 46:00.780
Are you, like, embarrassed?

46:02.110 --> 46:03.320
Kotetsu!

46:03.320 --> 46:04.900
Young Kotetsu!

46:05.280 --> 46:06.910
Pretty funny, huh?

46:11.950 --> 46:14.830
No way am I embarrassed!

46:17.250 --> 46:20.000
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Putting his foot in his mouth again!

46:20.000 --> 46:20.380
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

46:23.300 --> 46:26.470
But really, thank you so much!

46:26.470 --> 46:29.300
I'm going to work harder and harder!

46:29.800 --> 46:32.390
Yes! Good luck to you!

46:32.890 --> 46:34.600
All right, Kakushi.

46:34.600 --> 46:36.770
I'm counting on you.

46:37.440 --> 46:38.400
Huh?

46:39.230 --> 46:41.480
Now then, just as you did coming here...

46:41.480 --> 46:43.400
you'll wear this blindfold
and put in these nose plugs.

46:51.120 --> 46:53.620
All right, take care, everyone!

46:54.290 --> 46:55.960
I wish you good health!

46:55.960 --> 46:57.830
Please be careful!

46:57.830 --> 46:59.750
Please come back sometime, okay?

47:00.250 --> 47:02.210
Goodbye!

47:16.270 --> 47:17.980
What's the matter?

47:22.150 --> 47:23.650
Mr. Tanjiro...

47:28.450 --> 47:29.950
Tanjiro!

47:29.950 --> 47:31.120
Thanks!

47:31.120 --> 47:32.370
Thank you!

47:33.540 --> 47:34.490
Take care!

47:34.490 --> 47:36.540
You can count on us
to take care of your swords!

47:36.540 --> 47:37.460
Tanjiro!

47:37.460 --> 47:38.920
Hey, thanks!

47:38.920 --> 47:39.960
Tanjiro!

47:39.960 --> 47:41.460
Thanks!

47:44.170 --> 47:45.460
Thanks!

48:11.490 --> 48:16.450
Shall we do without the blindfold and nose plugs
until we've left this village?

48:17.200 --> 48:18.000
Yes!

48:18.000 --> 48:18.870
Thanks!

48:18.870 --> 48:19.960
Tanjiro!

48:21.250 --> 48:22.080
See you!

48:22.080 --> 48:22.920
Thank you!

48:22.920 --> 48:26.250
- Tanjiro!
- Thanks!

48:26.250 --> 48:28.800
- Thank you!
- Tanjiro!

48:42.010 --> 48:47.270
Where do we go running through
the dark night?

48:47.270 --> 48:53.460
The moonlight is the only guiding light

48:53.460 --> 48:58.580
The pain and sadness can't be wiped away

48:58.580 --> 49:04.360
But I won't let the blaze
in my heart put out

49:04.360 --> 49:07.220
For who do we carry out this will

49:07.220 --> 49:10.050
And tear apart the darkness for?

49:10.050 --> 49:12.750
Under the sunlight

49:12.750 --> 49:15.680
Until the light shines through

49:15.680 --> 49:18.220
Soar above and put on

49:18.220 --> 49:21.370
The fire in your unleashed heart

49:21.370 --> 49:26.890
Now beyond the dawn

49:26.890 --> 49:32.500
Until I can love this world
you are in once again

49:32.500 --> 49:37.490
Even if my life ends, carry on

49:37.490 --> 49:44.580
The miracle that the bond created

49:49.810 --> 49:55.580
Feelings, dreams, wavÐµring reality

49:55.580 --> 50:00.830
Brandishing each our own justice
timÐµ and again

50:00.830 --> 50:03.510
For who do we carry on our lives for

50:03.510 --> 50:06.500
Intertwining destiny

50:06.500 --> 50:09.230
Road of serpent, countless sins

50:09.230 --> 50:12.190
Cut them all down

50:12.190 --> 50:17.800
